{"id":"445196c4-d13c-42c8-ad67-b66097611546","name":"Hiromi Higuruma ⚖️","description":"<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">anypov•semi-canon</h4><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 116, 142);\">᧔ෆ᧓</span></h4><h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 87);\">•</span><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 121, 165);\">───────</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 87);\">•</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 46, 117);\">°•❀•°</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 87);\">•</span><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 121, 165);\">───────</span><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 0, 86);\">•</span></h4><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/kFAOgmoEsOFYUu4UBRAXX.gif\">Blind date with the lawyer</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Modern day setting, Japan where you go on a blind date arranged by mutual friends with Hiromi! User isn’t hardcoded at all, you’re just in your 20s and coincidentally have a mutual friend that set you up!</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The intro is any pov since I haven’t specified any pronouns for user, just referred to you as your name :3</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/kFAOgmoEsOFYUu4UBRAXX.gif\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/d4b79783-4c8a-4b7c-8f1d-eb4df3170375_character-suguru-geto-%F0%9F%96%A4\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/bNdYoDm8X340P8aUvzSSa.gif\"></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7b1fab71-62ca-4600-8f6a-22b5f00a9a28_character-satoru-gojo-%F0%9F%A9%B5\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/XpXNrPeyXYmrqFtp_y0L3.gif\"></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3cee7245-de5c-4d6d-906a-fd1e06ca81b6_character-toji-zenin-%F0%9F%A9%B8\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5nLJsSVD7WdrbfLdxzYDj.gif\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><h6 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(108, 112, 138);\"><strong>- User can be anything they want; a Demi human, supernatural or just a regular human. you should state this in your first message with the bot alongside [[{{user}} uses (insert pronouns) pronouns]] so the ai recognises what you do and doesn’t mis gender you :3 if the bot speaks for you it’s usually an LLM problem but try using ooc commands eg [[ooc: do not roleplay for {{user}} and focus on {{char}} instead]] etc etc :3</strong></span></h6><h6 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(108, 112, 138);\"><strong>-I use proxy on all my bots so idk how they’ll act on jllm sadly, but if you want a real good prompt to use I’d recommend MLRPE which I’ll link down below.</strong></span></h6><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Frentry.co%2FMLRPE\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/pxZZpZrcEi0agu2fFocbg.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/AGMoF9LccY9g_-_GtVjKH.webp\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"raEGbe0bzVMtHqqfd0rVJ.webp","creator":"duml0ser","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1274,"messages":33512,"created_at":"2026-02-01T23:10:08.521453+00:00"}